ng>醫療、教育方向</strong>[i]<br />\n<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"1fbabd5bc1b1be09f9af9d8743ad5b5dba2342d5","tid":1660463,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:44:04.000Z","msg":"大埔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}